about.title: About me
about.body:
I wish you to develop in the professional field. 
I have non-commercial experience with HTML, CSS, SCSS, Java Script, Type Script, GIT, React js, React-Redux, MobX, Rest API. I've worked with design systems like Ant Design and Bootstrap. I've worked with jQuery and Node.js, including making a site parser and a bot for Discord. Took courses Cisco: Introduction to Cybersecurity, Cybersecurity Essentials, CCNA R&S: Introduction to Networks.
 There is a military ID.
